anism, verified by the smart contract and the zkEVM, which is more secure than classical relayer-based bridges.\n\n### Helpful Links\nTwitter: [https://twitter.com/Scroll_ZKP](https://twitter.com/Scroll_ZKP)\nForum: [https://community.scroll.io/](https://community.scroll.io/)\n\n```\nVoting Options:\n* For\n* Against\n* Abstain\n```",
