      "content": "This is a temperature check in line with current Hop governance process 2.\n\n# Background\n\nAs discussed in the [Request For Comment](https://forum.hop.exchange/t/request-for-comment-amm-and-bonder-liquidity-incentives/352), [previous](https://forum.hop.exchange/t/an-effort-to-bootstrap-bridge-liquidity/226) [posts](https://forum.hop.exchange/t/discussion-liquidity-mining/257), community calls, and in [Discord](https://discord.com/channels/789310208413270078/989199841206882354/989199999223099414), Hop could benefit from additional liquidity in the bridge AMMs. Increased liquidity may attract larger transfers and allow arbitrageurs to maintain tighter spreads improving bridge rates for all users. Providing HOP incentives for Hop LPs has the potential to increase AMM liquidity significantly.\n\nIn addition, Bonder returns have been low or have required a high bonder fee percentage to maintain adequate returns. A multitude of recent bridge hacks have also raised the risk profile of bridges in general despite Hop’s strong track record of security.  As a result, bonders will need additional incentives if Hop DAO wishes to keep bonder fees low and keep bonders interested until a decentralized bonder network is achieved.\n\n# Proposal\n\nProvide 2,000,000 HOP per month to Hop LPs and 800,000 HOP per month to Hop bonders. The annualized issuance related to these rewards is 3.36% of the HOP supply.\n\n## LP Incentives\n\n2,000,000 HOP per month\n\n|Network|Network %|Network HOP/month|Asset|Asset % of Network|HOP/month|\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n|Arbitrum|40%|800,000|ETH|52.00%|416,000|\n||||USDC|34.50%|276,000|\n||||DAI|7.00%|56,000|\n||||USDT|6.50%|52,000|\n|Optimism|34%|680,000|ETH|51.00%|346,800|\n||||USDC|35.50%|241,400|\n||||DAI|7.50%|51,000|\n||||USDT|6.00%|40,800|\n|Polygon|21.50%|430,000|ETH|42.50%|182,750|\n||||USDC|41.00%|176,300|\n||||DAI|7.00%|30,100|\n||||USDT|9.50%|40,850|\n|Gnosis|4.50%|90,000|ETH|40.00%|36,000|\n||||USDC|31.00%|27,900|\n||||DAI|19.00%|17,100|\n||||USDT|10.00%|9,000|\n\n\n## Bonder Incentives\n\n800,000 HOP per month\n\n| Bonder | Est. Liquidity | Liquidity % | HOP Rewards/m |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| ETH | $12,000,000 | 57.14% | 457,142.86 |\n| USDC | $6,000,000 | 28.57% | 228,571.43 |\n| DAI | $1,500,000 | 7.14% | 57,142.86 |\n| USDT | $1,500,000 | 7.14% | 57,142.86 |\n\n## Retroactive Bonder Incentives\n\n800,000 HOP per month starting 6/10/22 (TGE)\n\n__June__ (Prorated for 21 days)\n| Bonder | Current Liquidity | Liquidity % | HOP Rewards |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| ETH | $11,300,000 | 46.27% | 259,112.59 |\n| USDC | $6,000,000 | 24.57% | 137,581.91 |\n| USDT | $2,121,816 | 8.69% | 48,653.92 |\n| DAI | $5,000,000 | 20.47% | 114,651.59 |\n\n__July__\n| Bonder | Est. Liquidity | Liquidity % | HOP Rewards |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| ETH | $11,500,000 | 49.04% | 392,286.99 |\n| USDC | $6,000,000 | 25.58% | 204,671.47 |\n| USDT | $1,952,218 | 8.32% | 66,593.89 |\n| DAI | $4,000,000 | 17.06% | 136,447.65 |\n\n__August__\n| Bonder | Est. Liquidity | Liquidity % | HOP Rewards |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| ETH | $15,000,000 | 62.50% | 500,000.00 |\n| USDC | $6,000,000 | 25.00% | 200,000.00 |\n| USDT | $1,500,000 | 6.25% | 50,000.00 |\n| DAI | $1,500,000 | 6.25% | 50,000.00 |\n\n__September__\n| Bonder | Est. Liquidity | Liquidity % | HOP Rewards |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| ETH | $11,700,000 | 56.52% | 452,173.91 |\n| USDC | $6,000,000 | 28.99% | 231,884.06 |\n| USDT | $1,500,000 | 7.25% | 57,971.01 |\n| DAI | $1,500,000 | 7.25% | 57,971.01 |\n\n[Github Link](https://gist.github.com/cwhinfrey/576e46ca7cb4a133b3dbb072ee2aa59f)",
